title: Start
body:
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher JiYeon>>
It's crazy that we're both allergic to apples.
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Me>>
And peaches...
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher JiYeon>>
And how both our pinky toe nails are split...
Do you think we're related?
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Me>>
No! Why would you ever think that?!
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher JiYeon>>
Anyway, let's unnecessarily overfill our bag with apples,
Even though we're obviously not going to finish them.
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Me>>
Okay!
<<BeginGameplay AppleGameManager>>
